Quick installation for Ubuntu 16.04 LTS:

apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv B58C58F4
add-apt-repository 'deb http://download.emercoin.com/ubuntu xenial emercoin'
apt update && apt -y install emcweb redis-server mysql-server
emcweb-setup -G -C -R="YOUR_MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD"

You have to change the 'YOUR_MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD' to your MySQL root password.
You can use outside installed Redis server and MySQL server. In this case please run 'emcweb-setup --help' to find correct parameters.
